# Repository Configuration Database - Whitespace-Delimited Plain Text Format
# Fields: repo_path branch_pattern exclude_patterns priority_files check_frequency last_check
#
# To maximize portability:
#   - Use relative paths (e.g., ./myrepo)
#   - Or use $HOME for user directories (e.g., $HOME/projects/myrepo)
#   - Use * for branch patterns to monitor all branches
#   - Separate multiple patterns with commas
#   - Edit this file to add your repositories for monitoring and analysis
#
# Example (edit or duplicate as needed):
./myrepo * .git/*,build/*,*.o,*.so,*.a src/main.c,Makefile,README.md 24 0

